**Query #3**

    -- =====================================
    -- 1. ROW_NUMBER()
    -- Unique ranking within each department
    -- =====================================
    SELECT 
        name,
        department,
        salary,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY department
            ORDER BY salary DESC
        ) AS row_num
    FROM Employees;

| name    | department | salary | row_num |
| ------- | ---------- | ------ | ------- |
| Bob     | HR         | 50000  | 1       |
| Charlie | HR         | 50000  | 2       |
| Alice   | HR         | 40000  | 3       |
| David   | IT         | 70000  | 1       |
| Eve     | IT         | 60000  | 2       |
| Frank   | IT         | 60000  | 3       |

