**Query #4**

    -- =====================================
    -- 2. RANK()
    -- Same rank for ties, gaps in ranking
    -- =====================================
    SELECT 
        name,
        department,
        salary,
        RANK() OVER (
            PARTITION BY department
            ORDER BY salary DESC
        ) AS rank_val
    FROM Employees;

| name    | department | salary | rank_val |
| ------- | ---------- | ------ | -------- |
| Bob     | HR         | 50000  | 1        |
| Charlie | HR         | 50000  | 1        |
| Alice   | HR         | 40000  | 3        |
| David   | IT         | 70000  | 1        |
| Eve     | IT         | 60000  | 2        |
| Frank   | IT         | 60000  | 2        |

