**Query #5**

    -- =====================================
    -- 3. DENSE_RANK()
    -- Same rank for ties, NO gaps
    -- =====================================
    SELECT 
        name,
        department,
        salary,
        DENSE_RANK() OVER (
            PARTITION BY department
            ORDER BY salary DESC
        ) AS dense_rank_val
    FROM Employees;

| name    | department | salary | dense_rank_val |
| ------- | ---------- | ------ | -------------- |
| Bob     | HR         | 50000  | 1              |
| Charlie | HR         | 50000  | 1              |
| Alice   | HR         | 40000  | 2              |
| David   | IT         | 70000  | 1              |
