**Query #6**

    -- =====================================
    -- 4. LAG()
    -- Previous employee salary in same dept
    -- =====================================
    SELECT 
        name,
        department,
        salary,
        LAG(salary) OVER (
            PARTITION BY department
            ORDER BY salary DESC
        ) AS prev_salary
    FROM Employees;

| name    | department | salary | prev_salary |
| ------- | ---------- | ------ | ----------- |
| Bob     | HR         | 50000  |             |
| Charlie | HR         | 50000  | 50000       |
| Alice   | HR         | 40000  | 50000       |
| David   | IT         | 70000  |             |
| Eve     | IT         | 60000  | 70000       |
| Frank   | IT         | 60000  | 60000       |

